rtant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-botto=
m-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Form 10-K</a> from February:</p><b=
lockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><strong>Greenhill is a unique global=
 investment banking Firm.</strong> Greenhill=E2=80=99s singular focus on ad=
visory services differentiates us from other investment banks, and enables =
us to offer best-in-class, conflict free service to each of our clients. Ma=
ny of our peers as well as the large integrated, or =E2=80=9Cbulge bracket=
=E2=80=9D institutions engage in commercial lending, underwriting, research=
, sales and trading and other businesses and investment management, all of =
which can create conflicts with clients=E2=80=99 interests.</p><p style=3D"=
margin: 16px 0;"><strong>Advising clients is our only business.</strong> We=
 do not engage in investing, trading, lending, underwriting, research or in=
vestment management businesses. Our clients=E2=80=99 interests are our sole=
 priority.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><strong>We provide unbiased, con=
flict-free advice.</strong> We have no products or additional services to c=
ross-sell and, thus, no inherent conflicts of interest. We also have no len=
ding, prime brokerage or other relationships with activist investors.</p></=
blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Oh, well, you know. If you are a se=
nior mergers-and-acquisitions advisory banker at a big bulge bracket bank, =
you will grumble =E2=80=9Cugh, we have all these conflicts, I have to cross=
-sell derivatives to my clients, life would be so much simpler if I ran a b=
outique that only offered pure unconflicted M&amp;A advice.=E2=80=9D (Or: =
=E2=80=9CUgh, my business is so simple and capital-light; <em>I</em> never =
lose the bank a billion dollars; why does my bonus depend on these risky re=
ckless traders?=E2=80=9D)=C2=A0And if you are a senior M&amp;A banker at a =
small pure boutique, you will grumble =E2=80=9Cugh, I keep losing business =
to banks that offer financing, life would be so much nicer if I had a balan=
ce sheet.=E2=80=9D Greenhill is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
ess.com/click/31560440.284426/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2Fyd=
GljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDUtMjIvbWl6dWhvLXRvLWJ1eS1pbnZlc3RtZW50LWJhbmstZ3JlZW5oaWxs=
